  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State has reasonable grounds to suspect that GELION BUSINESS TRADE is or has been involved in destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine, by making available goods that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine.\n",
